				<td colspan="2"><span>I was just wondering if anyone could help me out - I'm trying to find a list of atk, ac, and resist caps by expansion - someone had explained to me how the caps have increased as new content has come out, and how it's worth the effort to try to get an AC above the creature's max atk that you'll be fighting, and vice versa.  I did a search but couldn't turn up much info on these numbers, so if anyone knows a link or some of the numbers it would be very handy info.  Thanks</span></td>
